##Bile OD assay

# Define folder paths for replicates
folders <- c("BileOD_rep1/", "BileOD_rep2/", "BileOD_rep3/")  # Add/remove as needed

# Concentrations for rows A-H
concentrations <- c(1.0, 0.8, 0.6, 0.4, 0.3, 0.2, 0.1, 0.0)

# Function to process each plate with a replicate column
process_plate <- function(file, replicate) {
  media_name <- tools::file_path_sans_ext(basename(file))
  data <- read.csv(file, header = FALSE)

  long_data <- data %>%
    mutate(WellRow = LETTERS[1:8], .before = V1) %>%  
    pivot_longer(cols = starts_with("V"), names_to = "WellColumn", values_to = "OD") %>%
    mutate(
      WellColumn = as.numeric(gsub("V", "", WellColumn)),  
      Well = paste0(WellRow, WellColumn),  
      Concentration = concentrations[match(WellRow, LETTERS[1:8])],  
      Media = media_name,  
      Strain = case_when(
        WellColumn %in% 1:3 ~ "Low1-7",
        WellColumn %in% 4:6 ~ "Low1-9",
        WellColumn %in% 7:9 ~ "3-2B",
        WellColumn %in% 10:12 ~ "NC",
        TRUE ~ NA_character_ 
      ),
      Replicate = replicate  
    ) %>%
    select(Well, Concentration, Media, Strain, OD, Replicate)  

  return(long_data)
}

# Process all CSV files across replicates
all_data <- folders %>%
  map_df(~ list.files(.x, pattern = "\\.csv$", full.names = TRUE) %>%
           map_df(~ process_plate(.x, replicate = basename(dirname(.x)))))

# Check the result
print(unique(all_data$Replicate))  
## [1] "BileOD_rep1" "BileOD_rep2" "BileOD_rep3"
# Add 'Type' column
all_data <- all_data %>%
  mutate(
    Type = case_when(
      Strain == "3-2B" ~ "Parent",
      Strain %in% c("Low1-7", "Low1-9") ~ "Evolved",
      TRUE ~ "NC"
    )
  )

all_data <- all_data %>%
  mutate(Replicate = case_when(
    Replicate == "BileOD_rep1" ~ 1,
    Replicate == "BileOD_rep2" ~ 2,
    Replicate == "BileOD_rep3" ~ 3,
    TRUE ~ NA_integer_  
  ))
# Summarize data for plotting
OD_summary <- all_data %>%
  group_by(Concentration, Media, Type) %>%
  summarise(mean_value = mean(OD), sd_value = sd(OD), .groups = 'drop')

all_data$Media <- factor(all_data$Media, levels = c('Bile', 'CA', 'DCA'))
all_data$Strain <- factor(all_data$Strain, levels = c('3-2B', 'Low1-7', 'Low1-9', 'NC'))
all_data$Type <- factor(all_data$Type, levels = c('Parent', 'Evolved', 'NC'))

ggplot(all_data, aes(x = Concentration, y = OD, color = Type, group = Type)) +
  geom_line(data=OD_summary,aes(x = Concentration, y = mean_value, color = Type, group = Type), size = 1) +
  geom_point(aes(shape= as.factor(Replicate)),size = 2, alpha=0.2) +
  facet_wrap(~ Media) +
  labs(
    title = "OD vs. Concentration Across Media and Strains",
    x = "Concentration (g/L)",
    y = "Optical Density (OD)",
    color = "Strain"
  ) +
  theme_few() +
  theme(
    strip.text = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold"),
    legend.position = "bottom"
  )+geom_errorbar(data=OD_summary, aes(x= Concentration, y= mean_value, ymax= mean_value+ sd_value, ymin= mean_value-sd_value))+scale_color_manual(values = custom_palette)+scale_fill_manual(values = custom_palette)+
  guides(shape = "none",color= "none", fill ="none")
